divs: Sighting DetailsWe were out in the desert looking at wildlife. Lights appeared hovering over a distant mountain peak. Lights were stationary but each of the lights appeared to be pulsating. We watched the lights for about 40 minutes and then they disappeared.
Summary: Triangle of lights seen near Gila Bend.
